409
00:29:53.730 --> 00:29:55.730
! Hello!

410
00:29:55.810 --> 00:29:59.930
etc.

411
00:29:59.970 --> 00:30:03.770
tralala

412
00:30:03.810 --> 00:30:06.090
etc.

413
00:30:41.690 --> 00:30:43.770
Sa-mi spui înainte sa iesi.

414
00:30:43.850 --> 00:30:45.850
-Acum! 
- Stai putin. Nu înca.

415
00:30:48.090 --> 00:30:51.930
-Ma plictisesc. 
-Bine, iesi.

416
00:30:52.010 --> 00:30:55.610
! Daca stiam ca vii
as fi facut o prajitura!

417
00:31:03.290 --> 00:31:06.290
